        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "VEED is a top online AI video editor for quick, collaborative editing. It works entirely in the browser with no installation required, and offers auto-captions, screen recording, AI-powered editing features, and real-time collaboration tools. It's perfect for content creators and teams who need fast turnaround on social media videos."
